        <h3 style="font-size: 30px;">About Me</h3>
        <p>Hi, I'm Nicolle Capile, 23 years old, from Novaliches, Quezon City and I'm a 3rd year IT student of Colegio de Sta. Teresa de Avila and I was born on September 20, 2001.</p>
        <p>I have a diverse range of hobbies that reflect my love for exploration and creativity. One of my favorite pastimes is immersing myself in the worlds of fiction through reading books. I find solace and excitement in the pages of fiction novels, where I can escape into different realities and perspectives.</p> 
        <p>Additionally, I'm an avid fan of Korean dramas (kdramas) and anime. I enjoy the storytelling, character development, and visual artistry in both mediums. They offer a unique blend of entertainment and cultural insight that captivates me every time I watch.</p>
        <p>Beyond consuming content, I also love to challenge myself by exploring activities I once thought were beyond my abilities. For instance, I've recently delved into painting. It's been a fulfilling journey of self-discovery and expression, pushing me to embrace creativity in new ways.</p>
        <p>Overall, my hobbies are not just pastimes but avenues for growth, exploration, and enjoyment. They allow me to constantly learn, discover, and expand my horizons.</p>
    </div>
